      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
                    Kendall Taylor was an American art historian and biographer of American Social Realist painter Philip Evergood.  The collection contains original research material relating to Philip Evergood and the papers of Kendall Taylor, his biographer.</abstract>
